&lt;p&gt;My name is Rafa≈Ç Moneta and this is my programming blog. I am a college student at the Cracow University of Economics who does some coding in my free time. I am a huge fan of ‚ÄòChuck‚Äô TV series, football and running. My goal is to change the world by creating useful applications and teaching kids programming.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I created this blog for the purpose of the #100daysOfCoding challenge. I hope to write every day about my progress, what  I have learned and on what projects did I work. Besides that, I want to try to write some technical/tutorials post and improve my English and writing skills.
If you are too lazy to read my blog post about my coding journey thought #100daysOfCode you can always visit my &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/rmoneta5&quot;&gt;twitter&lt;/a&gt; for a shorter version. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wish me luck and I see you around. ü§ì&lt;/p&gt;
